  <FCP_Quest_GlowingOneContainment.questNameRules.rulesStrings.2>퀘스트 이름-&gt;격리 프로토콜</FCP_Quest_GlowingOneContainment.questNameRules.rulesStrings.2>
  <FCP_Quest_GlowingOneContainment.questNameRules.rulesStrings.3>QuestName-&gt;걸어다니는 원자로</FCP_Quest_GlowingOneContainment.questNameRules.rulesStrings.3>
